OL,3,CHighest number of race-related
OL,4,Cincidents on record reported last
OL,5,Cyear: figures
OL,7,FThe highest number of race-related
OL,8,Fincidents on record were reported last
OL,9,Fyear in Northern Ireland.
OL,11,FSome 1,411 incidents were recorded in
OL,12,Fthe 12 months from July 1 2023 to June
OL,13,F30 2024, according to the Northern
OL,14,FIreland Statistics and Research Agency
OL,15,F(Nisra).
OL,17,FMore faith/religion and transgender
OL,18,Fidentity hate incidents were also
OL,19,Frecorded over the same period when
OL,20,Fcompared with the previous 12 months.
