OL,5,Cyear: figures
OL,7,FThe Nisra figures, compiled from PSNI
OL,8,Fstatistics, indicate that crimes with
OL,9,Fa faith/religion hate motive saw the
OL,10,Flargest increase, while sectarian
OL,11,Fcrimes saw the largest decrease.
OL,13,FIt records that the number of race
OL,14,Fincidents (1,411) is the highest 12-
OL,15,Fmonth level recorded since the data
OL,16,Fseries began in 2004/05.
