OL,4,Cincidents on record reported last
OL,5,Cyear: figures
OL,7,FFaith/religion incidents rose from 36
OL,8,Fto 94 and crimes increased from 25 to
OL,9,F60, while transgender identity
OL,10,Fincidents increased from 61 to 73 and
OL,11,Fthe number of transgender identity
OL,12,Fcrimes rose from 40 to 41.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, there was a decrease of 254
OL,15,Fsectarian incidents, while the number
OL,16,Fof crimes fell by 317, described as
OL,17,Fthe largest fall in sectarian crimes
OL,18,Fover a 12-month period since autumn
OL,19,F2016.
