OL,7,FUnrest in Belfast and attacks on some
OL,8,Fbusinesses owned by people from
OL,9,Fminority ethnic backgrounds came at a
OL,10,Ftime of tension across the UK
OL,11,Ffollowing misinformation on social
OL,12,Fmedia after the murder of three young
OL,13,Fchildren in Southport.
OL,15,FPatrick Corrigan, Amnesty
OL,16,FInternational's Northern Ireland
OL,17,Fdirector, has called for political
OL,18,Fleadership to address the situation.
