OL,3,CHighest number of race-related
OL,4,Cincidents on record reported last
OL,5,Cyear: figures
OL,7,F"These new figures show that even
OL,8,Fbefore the recent orchestrated
OL,9,Fcampaign of racist violence in parts
OL,10,Fof Northern Ireland, the number of
OL,11,Frace-hate incidents reported to the
OL,12,Fpolice was at an all-time high," he
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"The fact that racist crimes represent
OL,16,Falmost one-in-a-hundred of all
OL,17,Frecorded crimes in Northern Ireland
OL,18,Fshould be a wake-up call to the scale
OL,19,Fof the problem now facing us.
